    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This example is a driver\u2019s specification, equipped with the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates to maintain structural integrity under lateral loads. The suspension retains its communicative feedback, and the M-Variable limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the individual throttle bodies and factory-tuned exhaust note remain sharp. A performance-first specimen ready for spirited use.",
