      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! This beauty has been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape for its next owner. It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so it runs great and looks even better parked in the driveway. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some fun adventures. Feel free to give me a shout if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
